---
// src/pages/banking.astro
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Banking - WinBet"
  description="Explore the banking options available at WinBet, including cryptocurrency and payment methods accepted in Madagascar. Learn about deposits, withdrawals, and transaction security."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#ffd700]">Banking at WinBet</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
      <p>
        At WinBet, we offer a variety of secure and convenient banking methods
        to make your deposit and withdrawal process smooth. Whether you're using
        traditional payment methods or cryptocurrencies, we aim to provide
        flexibility and efficiency for our players in Madagascar and worldwide.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        1. Available Payment Methods
      </h2>
      <p>
        We accept several payment methods, catering to both international
        players and those based in Madagascar. These include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Cryptocurrency (Bitcoin, Ethereum, etc.)</li>
        <li>Bank Transfers (via local banks in Madagascar)</li>
        <li>Mobile Payments (via local providers)</li>
        <li>Credit and Debit Cards (Visa, Mastercard)</li>
        <li>eWallets (e.g., Skrill, Neteller)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        2. Cryptocurrency Payments
      </h2>
      <p>
        We support a range of cryptocurrencies for deposits and withdrawals,
        including Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other major digital currencies.
        Cryptocurrency transactions offer enhanced security, low fees, and fast
        processing times. Please ensure that your cryptocurrency wallet is
        compatible with our supported tokens before making a deposit or
        withdrawal.
      </p>
      <p>
        To deposit or withdraw using cryptocurrency, simply follow the
        instructions on our banking page after logging in. Transactions will be
        processed promptly, and your funds will be available in your account
        once confirmed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        3. Local Payment Methods in Madagascar
      </h2>
      <p>
        For players in Madagascar, we offer several local payment methods
        tailored to your region. These include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Bank Transfers from local Malagasy banks</li>
        <li>Mobile Payment Solutions (Mvola, Orange Money, etc.)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These methods allow for faster transactions and a more localized
        experience. We work with local payment providers to ensure that the
        transfer process is as smooth and secure as possible.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">4. Deposits</h2>
      <p>
        Depositing funds into your WinBet account is simple. To make a deposit,
        log in to your account and choose the payment method of your choice.
        Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the transaction.
      </p>
      <p>
        Deposits are usually processed instantly for cryptocurrencies and mobile
        payments. Bank transfers may take up to 24 hours to reflect in your
        account, depending on the bank's processing times.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        5. Withdrawals
      </h2>
      <p>
        Withdrawals can be made through the same methods used for deposits.
        Please note that withdrawal processing times may vary:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          Cryptocurrency withdrawals are typically processed within 1-2 hours,
          depending on network confirmation times.
        </li>
        <li>
          Bank transfers and mobile payments may take up to 3 business days to
          process, depending on the payment provider.
        </li>
        <li>eWallet withdrawals are generally processed within 24 hours.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        6. Transaction Fees
      </h2>
      <p>
        WinBet strives to minimize transaction fees for all banking methods.
        However, some payment providers may impose fees for deposits or
        withdrawals. Any applicable fees will be clearly communicated during the
        transaction process.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please note that for cryptocurrency withdrawals, network fees may apply
        depending on the type of cryptocurrency used.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        7. Security of Transactions
      </h2>
      <p>
        The security of your funds and personal information is our top priority.
        All transactions are encrypted using industry-leading SSL technology to
        ensure that your sensitive data remains private and secure.
      </p>
      <p>
        For cryptocurrency transactions, we use secure wallets and procedures to
        safeguard your funds. We recommend that you use a secure and reputable
        wallet provider to ensure the safety of your crypto assets.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        8. Responsible Gambling and Withdrawal Limits
      </h2>
      <p>
        As part of our commitment to responsible gambling, we may impose limits
        on withdrawal amounts, particularly for new accounts or high-value
        transactions. If you wish to increase your withdrawal limits, please
        contact our support team for assistance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        9. Contacting Support
      </h2>
      <p>
        If you experience any issues with deposits, withdrawals, or have
        questions about banking methods, please do not hesitate to contact our
        customer support team. We are available via live chat or email at <a
          href="mailto:support@winbet.com"
          class="text-[#ffd700] underline">support@winbet.com</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
